> Using Mod_def2

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope T:
    output r content Mod_def2.S

scope T:
    definition r equals (output of Mod_def2.S)
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope T
┌─[RESULT]─ T ─
│ r = S {
│       -- x: [
│         Si {
│           -- x: 1
│         };
│       ]
│     }
└─
